title: Renovated,Large,Bright 2BR*Gas&Elect Incl. In Rent* Doorman* Must See
posting_body: ['Call Owner directly 718-268-7800 to see apartment', 'Gorgeous, totally renovated 2 bedroom/ 1 bathroom apartment in top building in Forest Hills.', ' Very bright, large 900 sqft apartment.', 'Contact*** Owner today at 718-268-7800 to set up appointment to see this week.', 'Apartment has been completely renovated , brand new kitchen with all new cabinets, appliances, floor and granite countertops.', ' Brand new bathroom with marble tiled walls and floor, new vanity and toilet.', 'Very large, bright living room with wood floors throughout apartment.', ' Master bedroom and 2nd bedroom are large and bright.', 'Apartment has a lot of closet space.', 'Great light in the whole apartment.', 'Apartment is located in a top, well maintained building in Forest Hills.', ' Building is an elevator, doorman building, and the laundry room is on the 1st floor of the building.', ' The building has an outdoor playground and sitting area, only for the residents of the building.', 'Close to all transportation, walking distance to subway, LIRR shopping and great restaurants.', "Must see, won't last!!!", 'Rent $3,00.00/mos.', '(****Gas and Electric included)', 'No Brokerage fee.', 'Available:  October 1, 2022', 'Contact Owner directly to set up an appointment to see the apartment.', '718-268-7800']
